A 40-year-old secondary school teacher is being held at Siaya police station after he was arrested for cohabiting with his form two student in Hono village.James Obonyo, a teacher at Hono Secondary School was arrested after residents told security officers that he had the schoolgirl in his house. His house is in the school compound.Chief Thomas Ojero said the teacher is said to have been spending nights with the student in his house.